id: monica-toolchain-decision
title: Adopt current Bun and Node 22 toolchain with constrained TypeScript
description: "Choose dependency majors that are current and mutually compatible, with explicit runtime and package-manager ownership."
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: bun,decision,node,toolchain,typescript
