author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: Declared engines satisfy all direct dependencies; type/lint/test/build pass; constraints and revisit trigger are documented
definition_of_ready: Registry engine and peer metadata have been queried for every major upgrade.
goal: trusted-monica-cli
objective: compatible-current-toolchain
value: Predictable maintenance without unsupported version combinations
impact: Avoids false latest-at-any-cost upgrades while closing known vulnerabilities
outcome: Current supported toolchain with explicit constraints
why_now: The security fix crosses multiple major-version boundaries
parent: monica-security-modernization
