close_reason: Compatible current toolchain adopted and enforced
body: "Adopt Bun 1.3.11, Node >=22.13, Commander 15, ESLint 10, Vitest 4, and TypeScript 6.0.3. Do not adopt TypeScript 7 until TypeScript-ESLint expands its peer range beyond <6.1.0; retain @types/node 22 to model the supported Node line rather than unrelated Node 26 APIs."
